# 3. 思い出すのは

Mizuki: *Sigh* Finally, a chance to sit down!
Mizuki's Sister: Thank goodness we were able to get a table. The food court was so crowded.
Mizuki: I know, right? This place feels like an oasis after walking for so long!
Mizuki's Sister: Haha. We did visit quite a few shops.
Mizuki's Sister: But I had a lot of fun. It's been too long since we last went out shopping together, Mizuki!
Mizuki: I had a lot of fun too! This sorta feels like old times.
Mizuki: Remember how we used to go out shopping while I wore the clothes you made?
Mizuki's Sister: Wow, that really takes me back! And we'd pick out shoes and things based on what you were wearing, just like today!
Mizuki's Sister: The way you smiled always put a smile on my face.
Mizuki: (Even back then, things weren't easy for me...)
Mizuki: (But I could forget about all that whenever I went clothes shopping with her.)
Elementary School Mizuki: *Sigh*
Elementary School Mizuki: (After working up the courage to wear the outfit Sis made for me to school...)
Elementary School Mizuki: ...
Elementary School Mizuki: (I'll be fine, right...? I mean, she said it looks really good on me...)
Classmate A: Morning, Mizuki!
Elementary School Mizuki: M-Morning...
Classmate A: Huh? Your outfit today...
Elementary School Mizuki: Y-Yeah...?
Classmate A: It's so cute!
Elementary School Mizuki: What...?
Elementary School Mizuki: Th-Thanks...! My big sister made it for me.
Classmate A: She did? That's so cool! It looks like something from a store!
Elementary School Mizuki: (Thank goodness... They think it's cute...!)
Elementary School Mizuki: Hehe. She made it using my favorite colors and these frills.
Elementary School Mizuki: We even picked out these shoes together.
Classmate B: Yeah, your outfit's cute...
Classmate B: But it's kinda weird that you're wearing it.
Elementary School Mizuki: What...?
Classmate C: Yeah, why are you wearing that outfit?
Elementary School Mizuki: ...
Elementary School Mizuki: ...
Elementary School Mizuki: Why...? Because...
Elementary School Mizuki: I like wearing these kinds of clothes.
Elementary School Mizuki: (What's so weird about me wearing cute clothes?)
Elementary School Mizuki: (Is it because I'm not like them...?)
Elementary School Mizuki: (But... There's nothing wrong with that, right?)
Elementary School Mizuki: (I just have on some clothes that I like wearing...)
Elementary School Mizuki: (This can't be right...)
Elementary School Mizuki: (But...)
Elementary School Mizuki: (I also don't want everyone telling me I'm weird or whispering behind my back...)
???: Mizuki?
Elementary School Mizuki: Huh?
Elementary School Mizuki: Oh, Sis...
Mizuki's Sister: What a coincidence. Are you also on your way home? How was school?
Mizuki's Sister: Oh, did something happen...?
Elementary School Mizuki: No...
Mizuki's Sister: Are you sure...?
Elementary School Mizuki: (I can't tell her...)
Elementary School Mizuki: (I mean...)
Elementary School Mizuki: (She made this outfit just for me. With her own two hands.)
Elementary School Mizuki: (Telling her about what happened would make her feel so sad.)
Mizuki's Sister: Mizuki...
Mizuki's Sister: I know! Why don't we go do some shopping together...?
Elementary School Mizuki: Huh...?
Mizuki's Sister: To help take our mind off things! I feel exhausted after a long day of studying, so I want to do something fun!
Mizuki's Sister: So, how about it?
Elementary School Mizuki: ...
